0x1000.png\"],\"isphoto\":true,\"glusrid\":\"56238099\",\"companyname\":\"Regent Bags\",\"mcatid\":[\"96454\",\"8422\",\"PMCAT 8422\",\"96454A\",\"96454P\"],\"mcatname\":[\"Kids School Bag\"],\"CustTypeWt\":699,\"dispflagval\":\"1\",\"iildisplayflag\":1,\"lastactiondatet\":\"2026-04-28T18:52:04.000+00:00\",\"catalog_url\":\"https://www.regentbags.in/\",\"usrpcatname\":\"Kids School Bag\",\"usrpcatflname\":\"kids-school-bag.html\",\"prdstatus\":\"40\",\"itemprice2\":149,\"itemcurrency\":\"INR\",\"moq_type\":\"Piece\",\"smalldescorg\":\"Kids school bag.&nbsp;It is&nbsp;used as a medium to transport different materials like exercise books, pencil box, water bottle and a lunchbox to and from school. Apart from this, a school bag helps a child to keep his belongings safe from external damage like sun, dust or rain.\",\"hotnew\":\"\",\"itemcode\":\"\",\"prod_multiple_photos\":\"\",\"original_title\":\"Kids school bag\"},{\"isEcomFlag\":\"0\",\"title\":\"Rexine Printed Kids School Bag, 20 L\",\"moq\":\"100\",\"displayid\":\"2854337817548\",\"datatype\":\"product\",\"ecom_item_landing_url\":\"\",\"ecom_cart_url\":\"\",\"ecom_store_master_name\":\"\",\"datarefid\":\"277977175\",\"isq\":[\"Color==Pink\",\"Brand==Regent\",\"Gender==Unisex\",\"Features==4 Zippers\",\"Country of Origin==Made in India\",\"Capacity==20 L\",\"Material==Rexine\",\"Usage/Application==Kids school bag\",\"Pattern==Printed\",\"Type Of Bagpack==SChool bag\"],\"photo\":[\"http://5.imimg.com/data5/SELLER/Default/2024/6/431035771/LH/TL/NN/56238099/kids-school-bag-125x125.jpg\",\"http://5.imimg.com/data5/SELLER/Default/2024/6/431035771/LH/TL/NN/56238099/kids-school-bag-250x250.jpg\",\"http://5.imimg.com/data5/SELLER/Default/2024/6/431035771/LH/TL/NN/56238099/kids-school-bag-500x500.jpg\",\"http://5.imimg.com/data5/SELLER/Default/2024/6/431035771/LH/TL/NN/56238099/kids-school-bag-1000x1000.jpg\"],\"isphoto\":true,\"glusrid\":\"56238099\",\"companyname\":\"Regent Bags\",\"mcatid\":[\"96454\",\"8422\",\"8422A\",\"96454A\",\"96454P\"],\"mcatname\":[\"Kids School Bag\",\"School Bags\"],\"CustTypeWt\":699,\"dispflagval\":\"1\",\"iildisplayflag\":1,\"lastactiondatet\":\"2026-04-28T18:52:04.000+00:00\",\"catalog_url\":\"https://www.regentbags.in/\",\"usrpcatname\":\"Kids School Bag\",\"usrpcatflname\":\"kids-school-bag.html\",\"prdstatus\":\"40\",\"itemprice2\":230,\"itemcurrency\":\"INR\",\"moq_type\":\"Piece\",\"prod_doc\":\"http://5.imimg.com/data5/SELLER/Doc/2024/6/430054058/EH/UW/YE/56238099/kids-school-bag.pdf#ITEM_DOC#\",\"smalldescorg\":\"Discover the perfect blend of style and functionality with Regent Bags' 20L Cartoon Printed Backpack. This lightweight, spacious, and waterproof bag is ideal for children, boys, and girls. Perfect for casual outings, picnics, tuition, and school, it's the ultimate choice for your little ones. Let them carry their essentials in a bag that's as stylish as it is practical.<br /><br /><b>Adorable and Trendy Designs</b>: Regent Bags offers school bags for boys and girls with cute, colorful designs that appeal to all children. These trendy backpacks will make your little one excited to head off to school or playdates.<br /><br /><b>Durable and High-Quality Materials</b>: Built to withstand daily wear and tear, our backpacks are made from high-quality, durable materials, ensuring they last for years. Perfect for active kids who are always on the go.<br /><br /><b>Comfort and Adjustable Fit</b>: Designed with adjustable straps for a comfortable fit, our backpacks cater to kids of various sizes. The ample storage space is ideal for holding books, snacks, and toys, making sure your child has everything they need.<br /><br /><b>Safety and Functionality</b>: At Regent Bags, we prioritize your child's comfort and safety. Our kid-friendly backpacks are designed with these values in mind, offering both functionality and peace of mind for parents.\",\"hotnew\":\"\",\"itemcode\":\"\",\"prod_multiple_photos\":\"\",\"original_title\":\"Kids School Bag\"},{\"isEcomFlag\":\"0\",\"title\":\"Rexine Printed Kids School Bag, 15 L\",\"moq\":\"100\",\"displayid\":\"2854337921891\",\"datatype\":\"product\",\"ecom_item_landing_url\":\"\",\"ecom_cart_url\":\"\",\"ecom_store_master_name\":\"\",\"datarefid\":\"277978218\",\"isq\":[\"Color==Blue\",\"Brand==Regent\",\"Gender==Men\",\"Features==2 ZIppers\",\"Country of Origin==Made in India\",\"Capacity==15 L\",\"Material==Rexine\",\"Usage/Application==School bag\",\"Pattern==Printed\",\"Type Of Bagpack==Kids school bag\"],\"photo\":[\"http://5.imimg.com/data5/SELLER/Default/2024/6/431028316/LL/SM/GN/56238099/kids-school-bag-125x125.jpg\",\"http://5.imimg.com/data5/SELLER/Default/2024/6/431028316/LL/SM/GN/56238099/kids-school-bag-250x250.jpg\",\"http://5.imimg.com/data5/SELLER/Default/2024/6/431028316/LL/SM/GN/56238099/kids-school-bag-500x500.jpg\",\"http://5.imimg.com/data5/SELLER/Default/2024/6/431028316/LL/SM/GN/56238099/kids-school-bag-1000x1000.jpg\"],\"isphoto\":true,\"glusrid\":\"56238099\",\"companyname\":\"Regent Bags\",\"mcatid\":[\"96454\",\"8422\",\"8422A\",\"96454A\",\"96454P\"],\"mcatname\":[\"Kids School Bag\",\"School Bags\"],\"CustTypeWt\":699,\"dispflagval\":\"1\",\"iildisplayflag\":1,\"lastactiondatet\":\"2026-04-28T18:52:04.000+00:00\",\"catalog_url\":\"https://www.regentbags.in/\",\"usrpcatname\":\"Kids School Bag\",\"usrpcatflname\":\"kids-school-bag.html\",\"prdstatus\":\"40\",\"itemprice2\":200,\"itemcurrency\":\"INR\",\"moq_type\":\"Piece\",\"prod_doc\":\"http://5.imimg.com/data5/SELLER/Doc/2024/6/430083313/VM/SS/KX/56238099/kids-school-bag.pdf#ITEM_DOC#\",\"smalldescorg\":\"Casual Backpacks for Kids<br /><br /><b>High-Quality and Durable</b>: Made with high-quality Nylon Twill, this soft, durable, and water-resistant backpack has a capacity of 13 liters, weighs just 355 g, and measures 29 x 35.5 x 13 cm. Plus, it comes with a 12-month warranty for peace of mind.<br /><br /><b>Spacious and Functional</b>: Featuring a spacious compartment with tablet sleeves for entertainment and work on the go, a side pocket for water bottles or pens, and an easily accessible front pocket for essentials like wallets, tickets, and cosmetics.<br /><br /><b>Comfort and Support</b>: Designed with padded back mesh and ergonomic shoulder straps, this backpack offers extra spine and shoulder support, minimizing the load during busy days on campus or while traveling.<br /><br /><b>Stylish and Trendy</b>: Perfect for Millennials and GenZ who value both utility and fashion. This lightweight yet durable bag is ideal for carrying textbooks, stationery, and lunch boxes, making it a trendy accessory for work, college, school, or travel.\",\"hotnew\":\"\",\"itemcode\":\"\",\"prod_multiple_photos\":\"\",\"original_title\":\"Kids School Bag\"}],\"search_urls\":[\"http://prd-search.intermesh.net:8985/solr/im-search/select?q=Kids+Unicorn+Polyester+Trolley+Bag&qt=mdc.search&fl=photo_boost%3Aif%28query%28%7B%21dismax+qf%3Disphoto+v%3Dtrue+mm%3D0+pf%3D%22%22%7D%29%2C2.0%2C1%29&boost=if%28query%28%7B%21dismax+qf%3Disphoto+v%3Dtrue+mm%3D0+pf%3D%22%22%7D%29%2C2.0%2C1%29&fq=mcatid%3A%2896454%29&fq=glusrid%3A%2856238099%29&rows=40&ps=11&debugQuery=false&start=0&_route_=oshard1%2Coshard2%2Coshard3%2Cgshard116%2Coshard4\"],\"search_time\":18,\"total_results\":8}"
